      <h2 style="padding-top: 6px">About the examples</h2>
      <p>
        Examples are the easiest way to learn how to create dashboards, forms, and views.
        This app contains more than 50 examples spread among various categories.
        Each example contains inline documentation that explains how it works, plus links to open the source code.
      </p>
      <h2>Example source code</h2>
      <p>
        The source code for each example contains comments explaining details of the implementation.
      </p>
      <p>
